    "## Ejercicio P13 — Clasificador de números con `match`\n",
    "\n",
    "Define una función `clasificar(n: Int): String` que use `match` para devolver:\n",
    "\n",
    "- `\"negativo\"` si `n < 0`\n",
    "- `\"cero\"` si `n == 0`\n",
    "- `\"par positivo\"` si `n > 0` y es par\n",
    "- `\"impar positivo\"` si `n > 0` y es impar\n",
    "\n",
    "Luego aplica esa función sobre esta lista con `map`:\n",
    "\n",
    "```scala\n",
    "val numeros = List(-7, 0, 4, 15, -2, 8, 33, 0, -1, 100)\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "Imprime cada número junto a su clasificación, alineando las columnas. Al final, imprime cuántos elementos hay de cada categoría."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 56,
   "id": "b3fe0d42",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "Número → Clasificación\n",
      "    -7 → Negativo\n",
      "     0 → Cero\n",
      "     4 → Positivo par\n",
      "    15 → Positivo impar\n",
      "    -2 → Negativo\n",
      "     8 → Positivo par\n",
      "    33 → Positivo impar\n",
      "     0 → Cero\n",
      "    -1 → Negativo\n",
      "   100 → Positivo par\n",
      "\n",
      "Total números: 10\n",
      "Positivos pares: 3\n",
      "Positivos impares: 2\n",
      "Negativos: 3\n",
      "Ceros: 2\n"
     ]
    },
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "defined \u001b[32mfunction\u001b[39m \u001b[36mclasificar\u001b[39m\n",
       "\u001b[36mnumeros\u001b[39m: \u001b[32mList\u001b[39m[\u001b[32mInt\u001b[39m] = \u001b[33mList\u001b[39m(\u001b[32m-7\u001b[39m, \u001b[32m0\u001b[39m, \u001b[32m4\u001b[39m, \u001b[32m15\u001b[39m, \u001b[32m-2\u001b[39m, \u001b[32m8\u001b[39m, \u001b[32m33\u001b[39m, \u001b[32m0\u001b[39m, \u001b[32m-1\u001b[39m, \u001b[32m100\u001b[39m)\n",
       "\u001b[36mclasificados\u001b[39m: \u001b[32mList\u001b[39m[(\u001b[32mInt\u001b[39m, \u001b[32mString\u001b[39m)] = \u001b[33mList\u001b[39m(\n",
       "  (\u001b[32m-7\u001b[39m, \u001b[32m\"Negativo\"\u001b[39m),\n",
       "  (\u001b[32m0\u001b[39m, \u001b[32m\"Cero\"\u001b[39m),\n",
       "  (\u001b[32m4\u001b[39m, \u001b[32m\"Positivo par\"\u001b[39m),\n",
       "  (\u001b[32m15\u001b[39m, \u001b[32m\"Positivo impar\"\u001b[39m),\n",
       "  (\u001b[32m-2\u001b[39m, \u001b[32m\"Negativo\"\u001b[39m),\n",
       "  (\u001b[32m8\u001b[39m, \u001b[32m\"Positivo par\"\u001b[39m),\n",
       "  (\u001b[32m33\u001b[39m, \u001b[32m\"Positivo impar\"\u001b[39m),\n",
       "  (\u001b[32m0\u001b[39m, \u001b[32m\"Cero\"\u001b[39m),\n",
       "  (\u001b[32m-1\u001b[39m, \u001b[32m\"Negativo\"\u001b[39m),\n",
       "  (\u001b[32m100\u001b[39m, \u001b[32m\"Positivo par\"\u001b[39m)\n",
       ")"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 56,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "def clasificar(n: Int): String = n match {\n",
    "  case x if x < 0 => \"Negativo\"\n",
    "  case 0          => \"Cero\"\n",
    "  case x if (x > 0 && x % 2 == 0) => \"Positivo par\"\n",
    "  case x if (x > 0 && x % 2 != 0) => \"Positivo impar\"\n",
    "}\n",
    "\n",
    "val numeros = List(-7, 0, 4, 15, -2, 8, 33, 0, -1, 100)\n",
    "\n",
    "val clasificados = numeros.map(n => (n, clasificar(n)))\n",
    "\n",
    "println(\"Número → Clasificación\")\n",
    "clasificados.foreach { case (num, clase) =>\n",
    "  println(f\"  $num%4d → $clase\")\n",
    "}\n",
    "println(s\"\\nTotal números: ${numeros.length}\")\n",
    "println(s\"Positivos pares: ${clasificados.count { case (_, clase) => clase == \"Positivo par\" }}\")\n",
    "println(s\"Positivos impares: ${clasificados.count { case (_, clase) => clase == \"Positivo impar\" }}\")\n",
    "println(s\"Negativos: ${clasificados.count { case (_, clase) => clase == \"Negativo\" }}\")\n",
    "println(s\"Ceros: ${clasificados.count { case (_, clase) => clase == \"Cero\" }}\")"
   ]
  },
