       "\u001b[36mpeorEstudiante\u001b[39m: (\u001b[32mString\u001b[39m, \u001b[32mDouble\u001b[39m) = (\u001b[32m\"Elena Sanz\"\u001b[39m, \u001b[32m3.9\u001b[39m)"
