       "  \u001b[32m76.49149999999999\u001b[39m\n",
       ")\n",
       "\u001b[36mpreciosSuperiores\u001b[39m: \u001b[32mList\u001b[39m[\u001b[32mDouble\u001b[39m] = \u001b[33mList\u001b[39m(\u001b[32m45.0\u001b[39m, \u001b[32m120.0\u001b[39m, \u001b[32m33.75\u001b[39m, \u001b[32m89.99\u001b[39m)\n",
       "\u001b[36mahorroTotal\u001b[39m: \u001b[32mDouble\u001b[39m = \u001b[32m47.31450000000001\u001b[39m"
