     "text": [
      "\n",
      "Palabras con 3 o más letras (ordenadas, mayúsculas):\n",
      "BIG | DATA | FUNCIONAL | LENGUAJE | OBJETOS | ORIENTADO | PARA | POTENTE | SCALA | SPARK | USA\n",
      "Palabras únicas con 3 o más letras: 11\n"
     ]
    },
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "\u001b[36mtexto\u001b[39m: \u001b[32mList\u001b[39m[\u001b[32mString\u001b[39m] = \u001b[33mList\u001b[39m(\n",
       "  \u001b[32m\"scala\"\u001b[39m,\n",
       "  \u001b[32m\"es\"\u001b[39m,\n",
       "  \u001b[32m\"un\"\u001b[39m,\n",
